Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡進行面向最終決議的公正交涉..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對面送來了個不得了的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.78,0:03:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿瑪利亞·托洛夫斯基
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是女演員的兵器經紀人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好一個超級美女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔻蔻·海克梅迪亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說有一位非常年輕可愛的經銷商小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就一直非常地在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 是真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.20,0:03:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請手下留情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這個..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.51,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have always stood on the borderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.51,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們始終踱步於境界線之上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:40.23,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm enjoying the view from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:40.23,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆因此境風景獨好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:42.85,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eeny,meeny,miny,moe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:42.85,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一，二，三，四...
